ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great if you want to learn about Haiti, Afro-Diasporic history in the nineteenth century, and a number of different subjects
Survey course on the history of Haiti from its colonial past through to the twentieth century. I would recommend this course to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned a lot about being an active participant in an academic community--something I feel Professor Eller models exceptionally well. This course allowed me to develop a broad understanding of Haiti that will benefit my dissertation/research.
